<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880203-0143 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News: Saztec International Inc. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> SAZZ WNEWS </CO><DATELINE> SAZTEC INTERNATIONAL INC. (Rolling Hills Estates, Calif.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Gary N. Abernathy, 47 years old, was named president and chief operating officer of this information conversion concern. Mr. Abernathy, formerly group vice president, succeeds Thomas L. Reed, 42, who remains chairman and chief executive officer. Mr. Abernathy joined Saztec when it acquired Information Communications Inc., formerly a unit of ICI Group, last May. Mr. Abernathy had been president of Information Communications. </TEXT></DOC>